Package ispd.motor.workload.impl

Class CollectionWorkloadGenerator

java.lang.Object
ispd.motor.workload.impl.CollectionWorkloadGenerator
All Implemented Interfaces:
WorkloadGenerator
public class CollectionWorkloadGenerator extends Object implements WorkloadGenerator
Represents a workload from a homogeneous collection of other workloads. Specifically, when used to host a collection of per-node tasks, the method makeTaskList(GridQueueNetwork) can be used to collect all per-node tasks into a single new workload.
